trans-unit.source: Encapsulates principals that are computer accounts.
trans-unit.target: Encapsula principais que são contas de computador.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ComputerPrincipal"></xref> class and assigns it to the specified context.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ComputerPrincipal"> </xref> classe e atribui-o no contexto especificado.

trans-unit.source: The computer principal account is not persisted when it is created.
trans-unit.target: A conta do computador principal não é continuada quando é criado.

trans-unit.source: To save the account, call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Para guardar a conta, chame o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A>método.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext"></xref> that specifies the server or domain against which operations are performed.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext"> </xref> que especifica o servidor ou domínio relativamente ao qual operações são efetuadas.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ComputerPrincipal"></xref> class by using the specified context, SAM account name, password, and enabled value.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ComputerPrincipal"> </xref> classe utilizando o contexto especificado, o nome da conta do SAM, a palavra-passe e ativada valor.

trans-unit.source: The computer principal account is not persisted when it is created.
trans-unit.target: A conta do computador principal não é continuada quando é criado.

trans-unit.source: To persist the account, call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Para manter a conta, chame o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A>método.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> that specifies the server or domain against which operations are performed.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>que especifica o servidor ou domínio relativamente ao qual operações são efetuadas.</xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>

trans-unit.source: The SAM account name for this computer principal.
trans-unit.target: O nome de conta do SAM para este principal do computador.

trans-unit.source: The password for this account.
trans-unit.target: A palavra-passe para esta conta.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that specifies whether the account is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Um valor booleano que especifica se a conta está ativada.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalSearchResult%271> collection of <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.ComputerPincipal> objects that have had bad password attempts within the parameters specified.
trans-unit.target: Devolve um <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalSearchResult%271> coleção de <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.ComputerPincipal>objetos que tenham as tentativas de palavra-passe incorreta nos parâmetros especificados.</xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.ComputerPincipal>

trans-unit.source: The time will default to UTC.
trans-unit.target: A hora será predefinido para UTC.

trans-unit.source: If you want to specify the time in local time, then specify the <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> property of the `time` object as <xref:DateTimeKind.Local>.
trans-unit.target: Se pretender especificar a hora em hora local, em seguida, especifique o <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A>propriedade o `time` objeto como <xref:DateTimeKind.Local>.</xref:DateTimeKind.Local> </xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> that specifies the server or domain against which operations are performed.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> structure that is used in conjunction with the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.MatchType"></xref> to find computers with bad password attempts.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.DateTime>estrutura que é utilizado em conjunto com o <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.MatchType"> </xref> para localizar os computadores com tentativas de palavra-passe incorreta.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.MatchType"> </xref> que especifica o tipo de comparação para utilizar na pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.PrincipalSearchResult%271> that contains one or more <xref:System.DirectoryService.AccountManagement.ComputerPincipal> objects that match the search parameters, or an empty collection if no matches are found.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the Service Principal Names (SPN) for the computer account.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de nomes de Principal serviço (SPN) para a conta de computador.

trans-unit.source: A collection of SPNs that specify the names of the accounts registered for this computer.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de SPNs que especificar os nomes das contas registada para este computador.

trans-unit.source: The syntax for the SPN depends on the underlying store.
trans-unit.target: A sintaxe para o SPN depende o repositório subjacente.
